Implementing this AI-Generated Comic Book/Storybook Creator requires multiple components:

Story Generation (LLM)

Illustration Generation (ComfyUI)

Integration & Formatting (PDF, Web App, or Print)

1. Setting Up the Environment
Install Dependencies
You'll need:

Python 3.10+

ComfyUI (for image generation)

Hugging Face Transformers (for LLM-based text generation)

Stable Diffusion or Custom SD Model (for AI-generated art)

Gradio/Streamlit (for a simple web UI)
